# ğŸ§  Brokins Insurance Chatbot

A production-ready, AI-powered chatbot built to assist users with insurance-related questions based on official documents and website content from **Brokins.fr** and its insurance partners (Cardif, APRIL, AFI ESCA, Generali, etc.).

This project uses a **modular Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)** architecture with **Google Gemini models** to provide accurate, document-grounded responses.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ… Answers based on real insurance contracts and website content
- âœ… Multi-submodel architecture for high-precision chunk routing
- âœ… Final decision model (Gemini 2.0 Flash) synthesizes responses
- âœ… Document chunking for large PDF ingestion
- âœ… Web-embeddable UI with image input support
- âœ… Language: **French** (100% localized)
- âœ… 100% digital and privacy-aware

